solution.p:
And the sum of lifting all of the slices from the bottom (x=0) to the top of the water level's depth (x=3) is
\begin{array}{cl}
\int_0^{3}(9.8)(1070)\left({\frac{16}{25}} \pi x^2\right)(5-x)\,dx  \amp  =10486\left({\frac{16}{25}}\right)\pi\int_0^{3} (5 x^2-x^3)\,dx \\
